{"tid":1649323,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"入黎話你聽點解唔好叫六大訴求","createTime":"2019-10-12T15:11:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-20T10:55:57.000Z","uid":284304,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d7e13d67dbdeb32459236c6e42c23bcba98b24b8","tid":1649323,"uid":284304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T15:11:22.000Z","msg":"就係呢個政府根本無資格接受新既訴求<br />\n佢完成五大訴求就要馬上下台<br />\n要點處置警隊係新政府既工作<br />\n<br />\n事實是即使彭定康來處理 也不可能解散警隊<br />\n解散警隊難以實行，整個社會撕裂即時進一步惡化<br />\n你地覺得呢屆政府可以處理到?<br />\n還是你們依然認受呢個政府的執政意志?<br />\n說白了其實只是宣洩大家對警察憎恨的一句口號罷了<br />\n如果呢種訴求係缺一不可 咁你地既缺一不可也未免太廉價了吧<br />\n<br />\n那以後又會不會有更多訴求?<br />\n取消緊急法,交出831cctv,徹查新屋嶺,遣返中聯辦?<br />\n醒醒吧 這一切能滿足你的 只有真普選後的新政府<br />\n沒有真普選的任何的&quot;訴求&quot;都只不過是滿足幻想的精神鴉片<br />\n希望大家明白 政治上的要求並不是你喊得越多就得到越多<br />\n而是用最少的喊價 得到最高的回報"},{"pid":"21c371c85da88791e65c3c0b7e1d868595da6b68","tid":1649323,"uid":11948,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T15:14:21.000Z","msg":"推，個人覺得維持5大好重要"},{"pid":"2cfc2513d338cbb19d7e04b6a9650876fe1ad491","tid":1649323,"uid":149383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T15:15:14.000Z","msg":"屌 大家加密啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b6aba015afaefd7d224c3c845349af2c928bf04","tid":1649323,"uid":80277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T15:15:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/10/12/pwbJYZ.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F10%2F12%2FpwbJYZ.jpeg&h=fea4b22a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/10/12/3DeFV2.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F10%2F12%2F3DeFV2.jpeg&h=11fde298&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"726d579bb66f520ee4df5f533d508e6d05505731","tid":1649323,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201